headline: KeyBanc Raises FY26 Estimates, Keeps Synopsys, Inc. (SNPS) at Overweight
summary: Synopsys, Inc. (NASDAQ:SNPS) is among the most profitable software stocks to invest in. On October 10, 2025, KeyBanc reiterated its ‘Overweight’ rating on Synopsys, Inc. (NASDAQ:SNPS) with an unchanged price target of $590, which implies a potential upside of nearly 35% from the current price.
